The project marks the debut of Hush Puppies’ first concept #flagship store in China, translating the spirit of the #internationally renowned American casual #lifestyles brand into a sensory journey. Rooted in the concept of “coming home,” the design balances the casual comfort of #domestic life, the gentle ease of a holiday escape, and the immersive #experiences of contemporary retail, articulating the brand’s ethos of #comfort , natural ease, and human warmth.

